# Crypto K8s Infra

Helm chart for deploying resources in a Kubernetes cluster.

## Installation

Build Helm chart dependencies

```bash
. ./scripts/build-dependencies.sh
```

Install the chart

```bash
./scripts/install-all.sh
```

## Components

### Crypto Stream Platform

Main Helm chart for deploying the Crypto Stream Platform in a Kubernetes cluster.

Has Sub-Chart dependencies for various components.

### Crypto Kafka

A Kafka cluster for managing and processing streaming data.

### Crypto Flink

A Flink cluster for real-time stream processing.

### Crypto Market Feed

A microservice for providing market data feeds.  
It simulates high data throughput by fetching data from multiple sources and producing it to Kafka topics.
